OL,7,FFour-fifths (80%) of people are
OL,8,Fworried about older friends and family
OL,9,Fbeing scammed online, with some
OL,10,Fbelieving that bank closures could
OL,11,Fpush more over-65s towards fraudsters.
OL,13,FBank closures have ratcheted up
OL,14,Fconcerns, with 61% of people surveyed
OL,15,Ffor Virgin Media O2 saying they are
OL,16,Fforcing older people to rely on online
OL,17,Fservices, putting them at greater risk
OL,18,Fof running into scammers.
