OL,5,Conline'
OL,7,FThe research quoted a 74-year-old
OL,8,Fwoman who was pressured into buying
OL,9,FBitcoin after seeing a deepfake video
OL,10,Fgiving the false impression of
OL,11,Finvolving Holly Willoughby.
OL,13,FShe said: "I was persuaded by what
OL,14,Flooked like a genuine opportunity, but
OL,15,Fit turned into a nightmare. The
OL,16,Fscammers were clever and convincing,
OL,17,Fcalling me every day and pressuring me
OL,18,Fto put in more money. In the end, I
OL,19,Flost around #20,000 of my savings
OL,20,F(some of which she got back)."
