OL,5,Conline'
OL,7,FMurray Mackenzie, director of fraud
OL,8,Fprevention at Virgin Media O2, said:
OL,9,F"Scammers are becoming ever more
OL,10,Fconvincing and anyone can fall victim.
OL,11,FFrom fake investment opportunities to
OL,12,Fmessages claiming to be from trusted
OL,13,Fbanks or delivery companies,
OL,14,Ffraudsters are always changing their
OL,15,Ftactics."
OL,17,FThe research was conducted by
OL,18,FCensuswide among more than 3,000
OL,19,Fpeople across the UK in September and
OL,20,FOctober.
